name: Sultana & Oat Biscuits Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 180Â°C. Line 2 baking trays with baking paper.
Combine dried apple, sultanas, rolled oats, desiccated coconut, raw sugar, each plain and self-raising flours and ground cinnamon in a large bowl.
Make a well in centre and add butter and eggs, stir until combined. Drop heaped spoonfuls onto trays. Bake for 15 minutes until golden. Cool on trays for 5 minutes.
Transfer to a wire rack. Repeat with remaining mixture. When completely cold, store in an airtight container.
